&lt;p&gt;Notwithstanding the details shown on the drawings hereby approved, detailed drawings showing the following modification(s) to the scheme must be submitted to and approved by the Local Planning Authority, in writing, before any work is commenced:
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
a) The proposed window design within the rear dormer shall be amended in order that a more traditional window design in keeping with the host building and the wider conservation area is achieved.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);&quot;&gt;REASON: To ensure that the external appearance of the building is satisfactory and does not detract from the character and visual amenity of the conservation area.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
